to convict you.

1026
01:27:17,032 --> 01:27:21,034
There was someone else there.

1027
01:27:21,036 --> 01:27:23,804
You're gonna die in jail.

1028
01:27:35,950 --> 01:27:38,318
( CLOCK TICKING )

1029
